- [ ] Ensure responsive design is maintained

## Implementation Plan
1. Add subtle shadows to the search container
2. Improve input field with rounded corners and focus rings
3. Keep the gradient button but enhance hover effects
4. Add smooth transitions for better UX
5. Ensure proper spacing and alignment
